Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.31,0:00:05.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3\pos(950,1060)}休息天怎么过？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.13,0:00:05.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\pos(980,1060)}昨天听你的广播了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.05,0:00:06.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3\pos(950,1060)}等下一起喝茶吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.00,0:00:06.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\pos(980,1060)}我也听了我也听了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.03,0:00:11.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个真的很可爱哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.69,0:00:13.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柚咲琳也一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.70,0:00:14.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好呀
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.71,0:00:17.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这场面要持续多久啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.27,0:00:19.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柚咲琳可是当红偶像
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.58,0:00:21.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会这样也情有可原
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.53,0:00:28.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.40,0:00:31.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概能猜到 但还是不知道为好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.55,0:00:32.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//----------------------------OPCN----------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.90,0:00:53.11,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}分崩离析的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.29,0:01:02.67,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}无情地发出宣告
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.00,0:01:15.53,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}你用双耳 独自聆听着什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.69,0:01:28.38,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}我的眼睛 映照出久远的梦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.59,0:01:31.73,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}选择什么 放弃什么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.75,0:01:34.94,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}我如何能 自行定夺
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.96,0:01:38.15,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}选取之物 早已在心
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.17,0:01:41.08,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}向神问询 是否有误
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.18,0:01:44.20,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}其实不曾孤独过
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.37,0:01:46.75,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}其实一直在身旁
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.79,0:01:53.82,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}现在 伸出手去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.96,0:01:57.06,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}已经无所畏惧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.16,0:02:00.57,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}哪怕化身怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.61,0:02:08.65,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}我一定 会做到
