Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.31,0:02:18.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先算理香的账
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.48,0:02:21.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再算由梨子的账
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.48,0:02:27.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,集体欺凌
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.12,0:02:29.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好惨
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.65,0:02:30.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.88,0:02:33.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毕竟她总会冲动地做那种事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.75,0:02:36.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,疼…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.98,0:02:42.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂…你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.55,0:02:44.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有意见吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.49,0:02:45.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明只是个看客
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.07,0:02:51.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟 协助者要来了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.86,0:02:56.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么受伤了？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.05,0:02:58.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被欺凌了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.03,0:03:02.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是该去趟医院？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.16,0:03:03.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,习惯了 没事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.13,0:03:07.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 就去「回礼」吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.61,0:03:09.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁去啊 麻烦死了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.03,0:03:11.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切 无聊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.43,0:03:19.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能力是 浮空
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.99,0:03:22.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好！出现了！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.41,0:03:23.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这个！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.92,0:03:26.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光临日本！？飞行类人生物现身
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.07,0:03:29.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个黑影就是他吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.88,0:03:33.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在还只是上灵异杂志而已
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.73,0:03:36.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但如果放任不管 事情就糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.36,0:03:37.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.61,0:03:39.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去哪？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.56,0:03:41.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是山里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.90,0:03:46.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我猜测 他正在山里练习飞行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.16,0:03:49.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直在那蹲点 就能见到本尊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.93,0:03:52.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直蹲点…要蹲多久？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.89,0:03:54.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然是蹲到他现身为止
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.94,0:03:55.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ＦＵ〇〇
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.81,0:03:57.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要让柚咲琳说这种话！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.99,0:04:01.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 先去超市买齐食物吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.00,0:04:02.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真要去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.89,0:04:05.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问…能不能变回柚咲同学呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.76,0:04:07.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种事由我来定
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.73,0:04:10.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我干嘛要听你的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.80,0:04:12.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你总是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.88,0:04:15.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这队人马能行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.24,0:04:17.90,note1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烧喽 烧了你哦 烧喽
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.68,0:04:17.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们几个 走喽
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.03,0:04:22.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,买这么多玉米干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.41,0:04:25.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烧烤怎能少了玉米
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.17,0:04:26.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烧烤？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.32,0:04:28.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么大的烟 一下子就暴露了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.60,0:04:32.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定能引得对方来找我们哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.71,0:04:33.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.85,0:04:35.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会有这种事？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.97,0:04:40.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再买些肉排 排骨 香肠
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.17,0:04:42.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 肉也买得有点多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.06,0:04:44.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃肉有什么不好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.07,0:04:46.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不不…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.41,0:04:50.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？辣椒？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.19,0:04:52.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辣椒可以提味
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.52,0:04:55.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要吃就你吃
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.73,0:04:58.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们关系很好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.01,0:05:00.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是在交往？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.93,0:05:04.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们刚认识不久 应该还没到那一步
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.90,0:05:07.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 看着他们就不禁嘴角上扬呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.36,0:05:11.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呀 我也觉得他们俩很配
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.25,0:05:16.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和柚咲琳肩并肩！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.74,0:05:19.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活着真好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.52,0:05:23.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.54,0:05:26.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男生拿帐篷和烤炉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.88,0:05:29.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和黑羽同学负责拿吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.66,0:05:31.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？帐篷…我们要住这？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.00,0:05:35.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都说了 要蹲到能力者现身为止
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.91,0:05:39.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…没带换洗衣服来呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.37,0:05:41.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不换衣服又不会死
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.44,0:05:43.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.70,0:06:00.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 到了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.51,0:06:02.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天黑前要搭好帐篷
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.78,0:06:03.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.21,0:06:05.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.02,0:06:12.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 那边很危险
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.84,0:06:14.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？哇！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.88,0:06:20.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么洞？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.05,0:06:21.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是口古井
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.50,0:06:23.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然知道就早说！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.63,0:06:26.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我觉得掉下去也挺好玩的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.64,0:06:29.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别拿人命开玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.96,0:06:31.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帐篷离这远点搭
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.72,0:06:32.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.72,0:06:36.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会好好把洞堵上的 放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.93,0:06:40.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 学生会要合宿
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.29,0:06:41.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我今天回不去了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.67,0:06:43.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？这么突然？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.29,0:06:44.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回不来吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.67,0:06:46.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.96,0:06:48.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？你没事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.53,0:06:50.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事没事 我很好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.94,0:06:51.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挂了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.72,0:06:52.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在下明白
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.24,0:06:58.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好方便
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.72,0:07:00.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别把人当打火机用
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.46,0:07:01.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真没味道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.77,0:07:06.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是怎么想的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.88,0:07:08.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也太显眼了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.51,0:07:13.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烤玉米真好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.84,0:07:15.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来来 一起吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.00,0:07:18.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切 换她来吃好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.86,0:07:20.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.45,0:07:21.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.13,0:07:22.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请用 您的烤玉米
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.55,0:07:25.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.65,0:07:27.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 真好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.99,0:07:32.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧是吧 烤玉米就交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.20,0:07:34.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来 吃肉吃肉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.85,0:07:36.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菜也要吃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.59,0:07:38.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,排骨好香！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.61,0:07:41.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,香肠脆而多汁！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.62,0:07:45.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别光吃肉 要和菜一起吃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.25,0:07:48.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 这肉超好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.17,0:07:49.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,酱汁也香
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.45,0:07:53.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果只有我在吃菜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.51,0:07:56.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都只吃肉呀 像姐姐一样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.12,0:07:58.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗬 是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.61,0:08:01.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呀 她特别挑食
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.58,0:08:04.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她…呃 你姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.72,0:08:06.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对你来说是怎样的存在？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.69,0:08:08.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.69,0:08:12.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐和我 性格完全相反
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.40,0:08:16.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她的男子气不输邻里的男生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.31,0:08:21.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是对我很温柔 我也很喜欢姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.70,0:08:24.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总是跟在她后面
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.12,0:08:27.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…哇 我说的好像有点多
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.75,0:08:30.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一说到姐姐 我就会激动
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.22,0:08:34.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里 我懂这种感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.04,0:08:40.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 敌人好多
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.77,0:08:42.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柚咲琳有危险了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.65,0:08:45.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的 请交给我来…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.78,0:08:47.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你小子一边去！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.26,0:08:49.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噢啦噢啦噢啦噢啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.66,0:08:51.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啊！我的表现机会…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.87,0:08:54.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们两个 已经忘了要干什么了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.98,0:08:57.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 她呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.65,0:09:11.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.04,0:09:13.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没 呃…那个
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.45,0:09:17.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是想问 你天天听的音乐是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.86,0:09:18.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.98,0:09:20.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是个叫ZHIEND的乐队
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.76,0:09:23.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没听说过
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.91,0:09:25.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是哥哥喜欢的乐队
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.47,0:09:29.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.03,0:09:30.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.63,0:09:35.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能给我听听吗？
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//----------------------------INEN----------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.25,0:09:53.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(200,200)\b0\fs52\shad0\blur2}Looking up high , found a steel tower
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.06,0:10:03.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(200,200)\b0\fs52\shad0\blur2}Wondering how I would feel if I fall down
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.92,0:10:07.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(200,200)\b0\fs52\shad0\blur2}Was it a dream?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.79,0:10:12.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(200,200)\b0\fs52\shad0\blur2}I saw deep red
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.45,0:10:39.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(200,200)\b0\fs52\shad0\blur2}Chasing , for what's far ahead
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.81,0:10:42.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(200,200)\b0\fs52\shad0\blur2}Always yearning
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.25,0:10:46.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(200,200)\b0\fs52\shad0\blur2}Don't know why but the beauty
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.40,0:10:49.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(200,200)\b0\fs52\shad0\blur2}I really want
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.63,0:10:56.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(200,200)\b0\fs52\shad0\blur2}May seem to be awkward to someone's eyes
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//----------------------------INEN----------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.94,0:09:50.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么？我似乎听过这个
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.93,0:09:54.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.91,0:09:58.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么说呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.47,0:10:01.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有种独自站在空旷处的奇妙感觉…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.68,0:10:04.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇哦 你很懂嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.97,0:10:09.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呀 ZHIEND的音乐非常非常宏大
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.78,0:10:11.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同时又十分寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.74,0:10:13.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或许是因为自行作曲的这个歌手
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.94,0:10:16.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,双目失明的缘故
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.61,0:10:20.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无限延伸的景象扑面而来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.63,0:10:25.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我现在在拍这种渺小的作弊狂魔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.58,0:10:28.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我的梦想 是给ZHIEND拍PV
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.70,0:10:33.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我从没见过的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.93,0:10:37.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追着ZHIEND拍个活动纪录片也行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.13,0:10:39.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 别拍渺小的我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.82,0:10:41.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拍他们去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.34,0:10:44.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我当然不会再拍你了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.87,0:10:49.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这曲子 连播放器一起送你了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.12,0:10:52.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？这怎么行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.90,0:10:55.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我做能力相关的工作 存了不少钱
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.61,0:10:58.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再买个新的就行 没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.74,0:10:59.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.52,0:11:01.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就收下了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.15,0:11:02.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.29,0:11:06.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两人一组 负责监视
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.19,0:11:09.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们先睡四小时
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.97,0:11:12.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后起来换班 监视到早上
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.51,0:11:23.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乙坂同学
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.16,0:11:25.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轮到我们了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.78,0:11:28.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 换班
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.22,0:11:31.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦…到时间了么…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.45,0:11:33.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又来…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.05,0:11:35.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那到底是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.41,0:11:42.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇！虹鳟！我钓到虹鳟了！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.06,0:11:45.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 看我钓个更大的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.82,0:11:47.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳟鱼 来条鳟鱼！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.45,0:11:48.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不能输
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.32,0:11:56.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 钓到了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.43,0:12:00.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虹鳟真好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.82,0:12:02.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柚咲琳同学 这条烤得很香
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.99,0:12:04.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老娘不是柚咲琳
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.99,0:12:06.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 还是让给柚咲吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.19,0:12:12.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我吃的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.53,0:12:14.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 请用
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.21,0:12:19.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 好好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.60,0:12:21.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶尔这样玩玩也不赖吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.47,0:12:22.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.54,0:12:25.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不会只是自己想玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.95,0:12:28.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问…今天也要住下来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.29,0:12:29.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 有问题吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.43,0:12:33.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好想洗澡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.39,0:12:35.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事 我准备好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.55,0:12:36.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.10,0:12:37.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请往这边走
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.17,0:12:38.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶…诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.02,0:12:43.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.97,0:12:45.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喏 毛巾和肥皂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.72,0:12:51.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,臭丫头 这是逼老娘出马啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.35,0:12:54.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男生那边由我来盯着
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.85,0:12:59.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有地方洗澡？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.62,0:13:01.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仅限女性
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.06,0:13:01.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.83,0:13:03.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男生请去河里擦身
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.16,0:13:06.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泡不到柚咲琳的洗澡水了！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.73,0:13:07.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好恶心！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.09,0:13:15.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…是穿衣显瘦的类型啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.92,0:13:18.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的能力 让我必须加强锻炼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.70,0:13:22.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使在校服下面穿着护具
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.65,0:13:25.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肉体也要改造得够结实 才能不受伤
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.13,0:13:29.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了使用能力 你还真努力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.30,0:13:29.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.20,0:13:32.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 事情不会与你无关
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.77,0:13:34.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？什么意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.82,0:13:40.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以后 你也可能会遇上意想不到的试炼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.00,0:13:42.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.64,0:13:45.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗬 只能入侵五秒
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.94,0:13:47.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种能力有什么用？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.72,0:13:49.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是你的…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.62,0:13:52.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…算了 没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.62,0:13:54.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？什么啊 吊人胃口
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.33,0:13:57.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戴着这么天真的面具
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.61,0:13:59.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定会为女性所困吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.78,0:14:02.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么恼人的话 我本来不想说的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.43,0:14:03.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 说得对
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.33,0:14:05.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为这能力
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.63,0:14:08.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我刚被有才有貌的女生甩过
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.34,0:14:09.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很明智
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.83,0:14:11.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恋爱之类的感情
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.39,0:14:14.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该在能力消失后 自由地感知
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.00,0:14:17.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底会在几岁时消失？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.87,0:14:20.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高中毕业时 应该已经消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.22,0:14:22.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有两年吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.99,0:14:23.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.19,0:14:27.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 对我们来说还有很久
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.98,0:14:30.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说 这水真凉…啊嚏！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.22,0:14:35.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真暖和
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//----------------------------TXTB----------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.74,0:14:42.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 和昨天一样换班睡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.31,0:14:43.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天是星期一啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.15,0:14:45.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要从这里去学校吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.55,0:14:48.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都说了 要蹲到目标现身为止
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.11,0:14:50.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太难为人了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.78,0:14:53.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞得好像在这里住下来了一样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.42,0:14:54.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是要这样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.91,0:14:55.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.56,0:14:59.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 我们就算翘课也不会影响档案
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.98,0:15:03.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算这样 我还是想回家
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.56,0:15:04.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妹妹在家等着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.87,0:15:06.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.78,0:15:09.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就先让我回家一趟 早上再来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.95,0:15:10.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.97,0:15:13.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先例一开 大家都会学你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.33,0:15:17.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且也不用担心
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.52,0:15:18.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.82,0:15:21.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕明天就能有结果了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.79,0:15:25.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又吃玉米啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.45,0:15:27.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.97,0:15:33.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们在这里干什么呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.79,0:15:35.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的出现了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.27,0:15:36.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是他吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.37,0:15:39.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 我们几个离家出走了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.22,0:15:42.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然各有各的理由 但是志同道合呢 哈哈…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.60,0:15:44.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又撒这种一戳就破的谎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.72,0:15:47.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说 你们要继续留在这里？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.96,0:15:50.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 我们想一直住下去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.58,0:15:52.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里很隐蔽
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.51,0:15:54.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是却被我发现了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.97,0:15:56.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们的家长会担心的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.80,0:16:00.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果报警 你也会被带走哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.39,0:16:01.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃？为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.09,0:16:04.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为 这是私有地
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.20,0:16:04.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.29,0:16:08.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(700,0)}（私有地 禁止入内）
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.73,0:16:09.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有这个
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.09,0:16:11.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这上面的 就是你吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.25,0:16:13.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.77,0:16:17.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,记录了你练飞光景的新闻
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.22,0:16:18.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飞？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.33,0:16:21.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁都能进的山里耳目太多
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.62,0:16:25.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而这座山就在东京 很适合你练习
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.27,0:16:27.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我们却在这里住了下来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.86,0:16:29.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全没有要走的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.87,0:16:33.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一着急 就自己跑了出来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.94,0:16:38.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了把我们赶走 继续练飞
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.43,0:16:40.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人怎么可能飞 你脑子坏掉了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.38,0:16:42.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我先报警
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.74,0:16:46.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个人来这种地方的你 也很可疑哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.92,0:16:48.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是来捡栗子的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.54,0:16:50.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这时节可没有栗子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.25,0:16:54.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 此时此刻你就在此处
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.63,0:16:56.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都录下证据来了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.76,0:16:58.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.31,0:16:59.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿过来 删掉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.95,0:17:02.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中了！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.47,0:17:03.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把井做成了陷阱？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.71,0:17:07.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 掉进无底洞后
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.84,0:17:09.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能用能力飞出来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.19,0:17:15.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实 我在井底垫了枯草来着
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.87,0:17:18.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托你的福 拍到大新闻喽
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.77,0:17:21.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,设下连我们都不知道的陷阱
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.03,0:17:23.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是个恶魔般的人物
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.87,0:17:25.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快拿来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.07,0:17:30.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乙坂同学 入侵他
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.58,0:17:32.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后我用瞬间移动打倒他
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.45,0:17:34.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那会很疼的 我不想啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.87,0:17:36.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.69,0:17:37.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到手了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.38,0:17:41.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他要逃了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.49,0:17:42.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.31,0:17:43.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拼了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.86,0:17:58.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高得离谱
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.34,0:18:04.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必须由我来控制
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.14,0:18:09.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停下来 停下来 停下来 停下来！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.51,0:18:15.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这赌博真凶险
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.67,0:18:18.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不说废话 赶紧入侵就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.54,0:18:24.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么玩意儿…到底是怎么了…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.93,0:18:28.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 大概有点摔伤骨折之类吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.64,0:18:29.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果还不错
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.53,0:18:32.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摄像机也完好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.62,0:18:34.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜你 你得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.52,0:18:36.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们…到底是什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.13,0:18:39.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也有特殊能力
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.23,0:18:44.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但这些能力只是青春期里的一种「病」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.49,0:18:45.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以后会消失
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.37,0:18:48.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一旦能力暴露
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.08,0:18:50.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就会变成科学家们的实验品
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.32,0:18:51.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不想这样吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.79,0:18:56.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果 你的能力恰好在飞行时消失 又会怎样？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.53,0:18:57.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你会摔死的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.36,0:19:00.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想为此赌上性命吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.53,0:19:03.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美砂 拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.89,0:19:04.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喏
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.57,0:19:11.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗…我还以为这是独一无二的天赐之力
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.18,0:19:13.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来不只我有
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.21,0:19:17.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我梦想过 有一天能在天空中自由翱翔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.86,0:19:22.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以「飞天齐藤」之名 成为好莱坞明星
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.54,0:19:24.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好矬的名字！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.42,0:19:26.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能理解你的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.30,0:19:30.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但以后别再用能力了 这也是为你好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.65,0:19:33.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.10,0:19:35.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.62,0:19:37.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平安结束了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.14,0:19:39.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 真费时间
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.63,0:19:42.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 说的没错
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.14,0:19:44.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.06,0:19:50.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到学生会的活动这么忙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.38,0:19:51.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.58,0:19:53.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥很优秀嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.76,0:19:55.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很抢手对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.75,0:19:57.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没那么夸张
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.87,0:20:01.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我呀 为了在学生会努力工作的哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.29,0:20:02.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做了美食的说！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.11,0:20:05.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蔬菜多多的杂烩面
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.76,0:20:06.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是红色
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.29,0:20:08.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.73,0:20:09.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能行！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.89,0:20:11.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开吃喽～  开吃！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.70,0:20:15.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好！！！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.31,0:20:17.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.08,0:20:19.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吃！好吃得想哭！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.86,0:20:23.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实我是想加点披萨酱调味的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.38,0:20:25.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但瓶里剩的不多了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.19,0:20:28.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然能做得这么好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.88,0:20:31.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别的菜也不用加披萨酱了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.21,0:20:32.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乙坂家披萨酱
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.08,0:20:35.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃秘传之物 务须世代相承
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.13,0:20:38.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我想去超市时
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.29,0:20:40.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知怎么就被警卫拦下来了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.75,0:20:42.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没能买到做酱的料
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.45,0:20:44.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警卫干得好！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.94,0:20:47.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我第一次感受到了搬家的美好！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.20,0:20:50.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 这样就够好吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.69,0:20:52.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用另外调味
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.71,0:20:55.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样我就放心了的说
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.23,0:20:56.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,棒极了！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.21,0:20:59.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于在实质上封印了披萨酱！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.93,0:21:02.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你身体不舒服吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.87,0:21:05.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事没事 我已经好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.70,0:21:07.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有宇哥哥不在时
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.62,0:21:10.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生了很多事 想说给你听呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.20,0:21:11.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.86,0:21:16.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我呀 冷不丁就被班上的男生表白了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.40,0:21:18.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？然后呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.40,0:21:19.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.97,0:21:21.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别吊人胃口
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.37,0:21:24.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很有礼貌地拒绝了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.59,0:21:28.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉 这或许是你人生的转折点来着
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.95,0:21:33.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？有宇哥哥难道希望我交个男朋友吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.55,0:21:35.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要看对象是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.04,0:21:39.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得比有宇哥哥更好才行
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.35,0:21:42.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 那种人可不多见
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.24,0:21:43.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.64,0:21:46.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.82,0:21:48.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是不是感冒了？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.13,0:21:51.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好烫
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.69,0:21:52.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有食欲吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.87,0:21:56.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的 我能吃完
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.57,0:21:58.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,37.8度
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.86,0:22:00.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是感冒了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.78,0:22:04.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去泡个澡暖暖身 然后马上进被窝
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.19,0:22:06.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得令
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.66,0:22:09.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.96,0:22:11.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡得着吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.82,0:22:13.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无碍
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.95,0:22:15.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 好好睡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.38,0:22:16.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.31,0:22:18.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白的说
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.71,0:22:29.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 只要好好休息就没问题
