Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.58,0:22:53.78,EDCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}今早终于寻获
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.91,0:23:01.31,EDCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(150,250)}俯瞰风景 铁道伸向天边
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.58,0:23:05.35,EDCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}刘海散乱飘扬
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.43,0:23:09.02,EDCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}待有强风吹过
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.11,0:23:14.88,EDCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(150,250)}吹走心中迷惘
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.19,0:23:18.83,EDCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}世界尽头的所在
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.87,0:23:22.46,EDCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}我们竟不知晓
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.56,0:23:26.15,EDCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}生命中的悲伤
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.27,0:23:29.84,EDCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}竟也无法摈弃
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.94,0:23:33.49,EDCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}继续向前走去
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.61,0:23:37.26,EDCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}终能寻获勇气
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.36,0:23:40.83,EDCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}梦却向我预示
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.97,0:23:44.62,EDCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}寻获既是结束
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.70,0:23:48.33,EDCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}天空改貌换颜
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.39,0:23:52.05,EDCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}群星流转不息
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.11,0:23:55.73,EDCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}待到梦醒之后
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.77,0:24:00.77,EDCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(150,250)}今日仍需前行
